{
	// A student cannot work with the same student in different projects
  /*
  all s1, s2: Student, p: Project | 
  		(s1 != s2 and 
  		s1->p in (Person<:projects) and
  		s2->p in (Person<:projects)) implies
  		one p1: Project | s1->p1 in (Person<:projects) and s2->p1 in (Person<:projects)
  */
  all s1, s2: Student | lone p: Project | 
  		(s1 != s2 and 
  		s1->p in (Person<:projects) and
  		s2->p in (Person<:projects))
}
{ all disj s1,s2 : Student | lone (s1.projects & s2.projects) }
{ all disj s1,s2 : Student | lone (s1.projects & s2.projects) }
{ all disj s1,s2 : Student | lone (s1.projects & s2.projects) }
